{"word":"H5809 - עַזּוּר - ʻAzzûwr - az-zoor' - Azur","slug":"H5809","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">עַזּוּר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʻAzzûwr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>az-zoor'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Azur"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>עזּר עזּוּר</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>‛azzûr ‛azzûr</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>az-zoor'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Azur or Azzur = \"he that assists\" <ol><li>a Benjamite of Gibeon, father of the false prophet Hananiah</li><li>father of Jaazaniah, one of the princes against whom Ezekiel was commanded to prophecy</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H5826\">H5826</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3270\">H3270</a>, <a href=\"#/H5826\">H5826</a>, <a href=\"#/H5827\">H5827</a>, <a href=\"#/H5828\">H5828</a>, <a href=\"#/H5829\">H5829</a>, <a href=\"#/H5830\">H5830</a>, <a href=\"#/H5832\">H5832</a>, <a href=\"#/H5833\">H5833</a>, <a href=\"#/H5834\">H5834</a>, <a href=\"#/H5836\">H5836</a>, <a href=\"#/H5837\">H5837</a>, <a href=\"#/H5838\">H5838</a>, <a href=\"#/H5840\">H5840</a>"}]}